# Android Configuration

This directory contains Android-specific configuration files.

## Structure

```
android/
├── app/
│   ├── src/
│   │   └── main/
│   │       ├── AndroidManifest.xml
│   │       ├── java/
│   │       └── res/
│   ├── build.gradle
│   └── proguard-rules.pro
├── gradle/
├── build.gradle
└── settings.gradle
```

## Setup

The Android project is generated automatically by React Native CLI. After cloning:

```bash
cd android
./gradlew clean
```

## Running on Android

```bash
# From project root
npm run android

# Or directly with adb
cd android
./gradlew installDebug
```

## Build Release APK

```bash
cd android
./gradlew assembleRelease
```

The APK will be at: `android/app/build/outputs/apk/release/app-release.apk`

## Signing Configuration

For production builds, configure signing in `android/app/build.gradle`:

```gradle
signingConfigs {
    release {
        storeFile file('your-release-key.keystore')
        storePassword 'password'
        keyAlias 'your-key-alias'
        keyPassword 'password'
    }
}
```

## Common Issues

### Port 8081 already in use
```bash
lsof -ti:8081 | xargs kill
```

### Clean build
```bash
cd android
./gradlew clean
```

